element.name: Complex Process with long Documentation
element.documentation: This is a very long documentation that is actually not necessary. It does nor really help to understand the model, nor does it explain something important. It just clutters the description and makes overall documentation much more complex than it needs to be. The information content relative to the length is just not justified. Often those comments are even poorly written.
